Choose 2. You may choose the same mode more than once;

* The next card you play this turn with an effect that deals arcane damage, instead deals that much arcane damage plus 1.
* Draw a card.

**Once per Turn Instant** - [Resource]: You may put an arrow card from your hand face up into an empty arsenal zone you control. If you do, choose 1;

* It gains +1 [Power] until end of turn.
* It gains **dominate** until end of turn. *(The defending hero can't defend the attack with more than 1 card from their hand.)*
